data.description: Screened patio with pool overlooking water. Walking distance to elementary, middle and high schools. Near Okeeheelee park. Walking and jogging paths.  Manned 24/7 security gate. Basketball courts, playground, picnic pavillon and open athletic field. Excellent fishing from backyard. Wildlife galore. Intercom system throughout house.  Central vaccum system. 2 car garage with space for 2 cars in driveway. Accordian hurricane shutters on windows. Access to pool and patio from Master bedroom. Security system. Solar heated pool. Upgraded ac unit in 2011.
data.whatILove: Perfect home for a family. Side yard is large enough for play gym. Fire pit area. Close to Okeeheelee park and shopping.
